    bibo:volume "4126" ;
    dc:creator "Li, Chun-Lin; Yang, Ping-Shih; Wang, Chuan-Chan" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of Megistophylla Burmeister (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Melolonthinae) from Taiwan, with notes on the genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258600>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258599>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258601>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258602> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258600>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 6. Close view of dorsum of male Megistophylla (3, 5 head and anterior half of pronotum; 4, 6 basal half of pronotum, scutellum. and elytra). 3 – 4. Megistophylla formosana new species; 5 – 6. Megistophylla xitoui new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258600/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258599>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Dorsal habitus of male Megistophylla. 1. Megistophylla formosana new species, holotype; 2. Megistophylla xitoui new species, holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258599/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258601>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 8. Ventral view of protarsomeres 2 – 3 of Megistophylla. 7. Megistophylla formosana new species; 8. Megistophylla xitoui new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258601/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258602>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Parameres of Megistophylla. (9, 11, lateral view; 10, 12, dorsal view). 9 – 10. Megistophylla formosana new species; 11 – 12. Megistophylla xitoui new species. Scale bar = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258602/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

